@support_peoples_party
title: 为「人民党」构建支持
subtitle: 我们能否将党的基础扩展到工业工人阶级之外？
view-if: peoples_party = 0
choose-if: peoples_party_support <= 4 and advisor_action_timer = 0 and peoples_party = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : 距离下次顾问行动还需 [+ advisor_action_timer +] 个月。 ?][? if peoples_party_support > 4: 「人民党」的支持已相当可观。 ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; peoples_party_support += 1; reformist_strength += 5;

我们正在积累对「人民党」理念的支持。

@build_peoples_party
title: 建立「人民党」
subtitle: 我们能否将党的基础扩展到工业工人阶级之外？
view-if: peoples_party = 0
choose-if: peoples_party_support >= 3 and advisor_action_timer = 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : 距离下次顾问行动还需 [+ advisor_action_timer +] 个月。 ?][? if peoples_party_support < 3: 党内对此政策的支持尚不足。 ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1
go-to: peoples_party

